flowRoot.flowPara: Loose wiring in sensor/reactor interfaces can cause system instability
Sensor wiring should be routed around the damaged connection
Ensure that EPS NODE B is connected to BACKUP DATA BUS 14
DATA CONDUIT socket P45 should be connected to CONTROL/NAV BYPASS socket PDER
Route CONTROL/NAV BYPASS PANEL socket DF/F to EPS NODE A
This ship is equipped with an Emergency System Repair Kit. In your vessel it is located behind the tactical officers chair
